   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.640", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass alle politischen Ebenen f\u00fcr die Bildungsrepublik zusammenwirken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.760", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit wir es f\u00fcr die Kinder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.760", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Jugendlichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.240", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Eltern und diejenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.880", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die die Bildung mit ganzem Herzblut organisieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.320", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gut einrichten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.760", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das kann man auch konkreter machen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.280", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann es konkret machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.680", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir uns jetzt fragen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.320", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie schaffen wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.080", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "alle Beteiligten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.800", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Jahrzehntsaufgabe \u201eGute Ganztagsschule in Deutschland\u201c? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.160", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da reden wir nicht \u00fcber 100\u00a0Millionen Euro; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.160", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da reden wir \u00fcber 5 bis 6\u00a0Milliarden Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.800", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie schaffen wir es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.080", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die digitale Modernisierung in den Schulen zu erm\u00f6glichen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.480", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da ist Frau Wanka schon mit 5\u00a0Milliarden Euro\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.200", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so das Versprechen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.840", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Vorlage gegangen,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.880", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat aber bisher nichts geliefert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.560", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielleicht hat sie nichts geliefert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.720", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil Innenpolitiker der CDU sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.600", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Artikel\u00a091c Grundgesetz gibt gar keine Grundlage daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.120", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dies f\u00fcr eine schulische Verbesserung zu verwenden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.080", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie von der CDU/CSU sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.240", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen in Deutschland die berufliche Bildung ert\u00fcchtigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.960", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil das sehr notwendig ist,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.720", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und daf\u00fcr wollen wir die beruflichen Schulen f\u00f6rdern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.080", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gleichzeitig sagen Sie: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.800", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben keine Kompetenz f\u00fcr die beruflichen Schulen;"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.120", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist Landesgesetzgebung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.200", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.320", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie sich mal ein bisschen auf die Fakten einlassen w\u00fcrden! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.600", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben hier \u00fcber das Berufsbildungsgesetz die Kompetenz in Bezug auf die betriebliche Ausbildung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.760", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nicht in Bezug auf die beruflichen Schulen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.200", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir finden es gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.520", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie begriffen haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.600", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man dort zusammen etwas schaffen muss."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.080", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber dann stehen doch die Inhalte vorn und nicht der Gesetzesparagraf."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.120", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir waren froh und haben gedacht: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.600", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alle n\u00e4hern sich dem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.560", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was die Menschen bewegt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.320", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gute Schule mit gleichen Chancen f\u00fcr alle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.520", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit Langfristigkeit und mit Fairness in der Finanzierung\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.760", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das bei erwarteten 1\u00a0Million zus\u00e4tzlichen Sch\u00fclerinnen und Sch\u00fclern.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.880", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.680", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dort Fairness in der Finanzierung herzustellen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.720", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "darf man vielleicht noch in Erinnerung bringen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.880", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass aktuell die L\u00e4nder \u00fcber 80\u00a0Prozent von dem investieren und bezahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.760", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was an Schulen geleistet wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.400", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Kommunen kommen dann schon als N\u00e4chstes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.080", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dann kommt der Bund. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.200", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Bund leistet dabei nicht nur einen Ausgleich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.840", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht nur eine Unterst\u00fctzung bei gro\u00dfen Projekten; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.120", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "er ist manchmal auch stimulierend t\u00e4tig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.320", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.480", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
