   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.320", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber es geschah eigentlich im luftleeren Raum."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.640", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.800", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was wir jetzt mit Ihrem Ansto\u00df zusammen schaffen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.240", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.840", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Impuls aus dem Bundesrat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.400", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Impuls von immer mehr L\u00e4ndern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.960", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
