   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.360", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aufgenommen wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.200", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr werben wir. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.320", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werben so daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.400", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir es schon in anderer Situation getan haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.960", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben nach 2006 die Hochschulpakte erm\u00f6glicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.720", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben 2008, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.960", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der Kata\u00adstrophensituation mit Lehman Brothers, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.520", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Konjunkturprogramme f\u00fcr Schulen m\u00f6glich gemacht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.440", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben 2014 erstmals in der Geschichte des Grundgesetzes die Lehre durch den Bund f\u00f6rderf\u00e4hig gemacht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.720", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben 2017 die finanzschwachen Kommunen als f\u00f6rderf\u00e4hig erkannt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.840", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.960", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In dieser langen Geschichte braucht es jetzt einen Befreiungsschlag. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.640", 
   "id": "s000091", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da, "
   ]
  }, 
